    <JadeMethod name="setMyTAViewInterface" id="e247f5c5-2d0e-4ff7-9a24-fc22ee24aa24">
        <updating/>
        <source>setMyTAViewInterface(_taViewInterface : IF_CM_TerminalAreaViews) updating, protected;
/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		


Date		Who		Reason
